    Class Description
    Command

    CommandCreateGame
    Used to create the game
    CommandDescription
    Used to obtain the god description
    CommandHelp
    Used to show the complete list of command
    CommandInteract
    Used to activate or deactivate the god power
    CommandJoinGame
    Used to join a game
    CommandPlaceWorker
    Used to place worker
    CommandReload

    CommandSelect

    CommandSelectPower
    Used to select god from a given list
    CommandSelectStartingPlayer
    Used to select the starting player
    CommandSelectWorker
    Used to select worker
    CommandSetName
    Used to set a player username
    CommandSurrender
    Used to forfeit the game
    CommandUndo
    Used to go back to the beginning of the current turn
